data.description: Enjoy relaxed Palm Beach living with this beautiful 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms Single Family Home with a nice sized loft that can be converted into a 4th bedroom. Enjoy a mosquito free summer afternoon in this screened pool area while BBQ outback in the fenced backyard. The home has been upgraded with a new Pool pump, A/C unit, Water Heater and Garage Opener. Rivermill is a stunning gated community offering 24 hour security. The community has several great amenities such as the clubhouse, pool & picnic area, volleyball, basketball, fitness center, playground and with easy access to these amenities will make you never want to leave the community. Minutes away from great shopping, restaurants, I-95 & the Turnpike.The only thing that this home is missing is... you!
